{{zh-forms|[[病]][[来]][[如]][[山]][[倒]]，[[病]][[去]][[如]][[抽]][[丝]]|[[病來如山倒，病去如抽絲]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' bìng lái rú shān dăo, bìng qù rú chōu sī)
# Sickness comes like an avalanche but goes like reeling silk / illness strikes like a landslide, recovery is as slow as reeling silk.
